title: West Branch beats Alburnett remains unbeaten
text:
West Branch beats Alburnett remains unbeaten Posted: Friday Night Heroes Catch all the high school football highlights during the regular season and playoffs, get live score updates and vote for the Play of the Week and the Game of the Week! More >> Catch all the high school football highlights during the regular season and playoffs, get live score updates and vote for the Play of the Week and the Game of the Week! More >> 
West Branch takes on Alburnett in the first quarter and first and goal Bears Luke Leonchs scores up the middle 7-0 lead. 
Pirates respond on 1st and goal quarterback Dillon Caves on the keeper ties it at 7. 
2nd q. There's a Bear in the air quarterback Cooper Koening airs it out to John Sawher and he scores 14-7 West Branch. 
Then on 2nd and goal Leonchs scores on another run play to make it 21-7 at the half. West Branch wins 24-14.
